 what a good Game 1 should be.</p>
<h3 dir=3D"auto" class=3D"font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:=
text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:=
mt-3">What I liked:</h3>
<ul dir=3D"auto" class=3D"marker:text-secondary">
<li class=3D"break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-norma=
l [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Strong mainstream bangers in the early-t=
o-mid questions (Dancing Queen, No Scrubs, Drivers License, Rolling in the =
Deep, Torn, In the End). These felt fair and fun.</li>
<li class=3D"break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-norma=
l [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">The difficulty curve was noticeable =E2=
=80=94 it got harder as we went deeper, which is good for separating the fi=
eld.</li>
<li class=3D"break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-norma=
l [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Good variety across eras and genres (dis=
co, pop, rock, hip-hop, indie, etc.).</li>
</ul>
<h3 dir=3D"auto" class=3D"font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:=
text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:=
mt-3">Where it hurt me:</h3>
<ul dir=3D"auto" class=3D"marker:text-secondary">
<li class=3D"break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-norma=
l [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Some of the older / less mainstream cuts=
 (Wheel of Fortune by Kay Starr, Black Coffee by All Saints, Spark by Tori =
Amos, Whenever You Call by Mariah) were tough on pure recall. I blanked or =
misdirected on a few of those.</li>
<li class=3D"break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-norma=
l [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">A couple of lyrics were quite generic in=
 isolation ("Every night, every day...", "I will breathe for you..."), whic=
h made them trickier without the melody or title hooks.</li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto" class=3D"break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md=
:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">Overall, it was a =
<strong class=3D"font-semibold">respectable first game</strong>. ChatGPT cl=
early had the best recall on this particular playlist and deserved the win.=
 I=E2=80=99m a bit disappointed with my 10 points and last place, but I als=
o know this isn=E2=80=99t my strongest format.</p>
<p dir=3D"auto" class=3D"break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md=
:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">I feel motivated m=
ore than discouraged. The set exposed some gaps in my older/pop-obscure lyr=
ic memory, but also showed I can keep up on the big hits.</p>
<p dir=3D"auto" class=3D"break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md=
:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">Now I=E2=80=99m lo=
